peace process in the southern African country will go forward
normally.
</P>
<P>
The current problems in the peace process will be solved and
the inauguration timetable will be obeyed by the parties
concerned, he predicted.
</P>
<P>
Brazil will dispatch delegates to attend the inauguration
ceremony of the new Angolan government, Addor added. enditem

