china wishes to probe new ways of cooperation together with
the Ugandan side so that economic cooperation between the two
countries can be raised to a new level, he noted.
</P>
<P>
Before the meeting, the two sides signed an agreement on
economic and technical cooperation between the two countries.
</P>
