China's WTO membership could increase bargaining power of the
region to negotiate on trade issues with the United States and the
European Union, said the minister.
</P>
<P>
Narongchai said China will eventually play a bigger role within
the Asia Pacific Economic Cooperation (APEC) forum and in the
Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN).
</P>
<P>
He also said that Thailand is going to open a new chapter of
economic relations with China and increase cooperation on trade
and investment. 
