<HEADLINE> Output of Major Light Industrial Products </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 4 (Xinhua) -- China's light industry generated
1,193.8 billion yuan in added value in 1996, up by 13.1 percent
over the previous year.
</P>
<P>
Due to the changes in the market demand, there were increases
and decreases in the production of key light industrial products.
