reached 374.5 billion yuan, an increase of 13.5 percent, or 0.4
percentage points higher than the growth in the previous year,
while that for real estate was 382.5 billion yuan, up 21.5
percent, or 1.8 percentage points lower than the growth in the
previous year. 
